{"tid":309591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去博物館參觀啲人正職係咪超市格價員？","createTime":"2017-07-05T07:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T17:59:13.000Z","uid":8274,"like":366,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec630e62fbfa4aa709b2de6af395ccbb338d494","tid":309591,"uid":8274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"件件展品都一要貼晒埋去影，影少張一世都唔會攞返出嚟睇既相好似蝕晒底咁<br />\n通常都係啲五六十歲廢中，用手機放到大一大咁影<br />\n唔影當自己冇嚟過，影左又以為自己擁有左，平時又唔見對文化咁有興趣<br />\n啲細路又嘈又要四圍走<br />\n行博物館真係好感受到香港人喧鬧冇教養既水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e5fefd57338007b72900500e52c778de1d545d","tid":309591,"uid":64953,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br />\n去外國博物館未見過香港人"},{"pid":"c7129466d43cf268ed0d64a6aeca7f20d1831717","tid":309591,"uid":64576,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:05:53.000Z","msg":"巴打你係咪去埃及展覽?"},{"pid":"a35767a8e610e50379fdc118a1c3877ee8c71443","tid":309591,"uid":55770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你係咪去埃及展覽?</blockquote><br />\n屌 正想講 班師狗學生哥係撚咁影 連打caption個陣都唔撚讓個位出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c8374f8fceeac8c623e11f29714dca1647e81a","tid":309591,"uid":64576,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打你係咪去埃及展覽?</blockquote><br />\n屌 正想講 班師狗學生哥係撚咁影 連打caption個陣都唔撚讓個位出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要用閃光燈影<br />\n又用隻手長時間掂住個展櫃<br />\n真心痴撚線"},{"pid":"12c396ac3962c1a45cad20552f31759dc6da4bde","tid":309591,"uid":52605,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"博物館唔係所有嘢都可以影"},{"pid":"7b5594faa0c58703e1b2a5ed2ea3326fc074ba20","tid":309591,"uid":8274,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:34:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你係咪去埃及展覽?</blockquote><br />\n個個展覽都係啦<br />\n羅浮宮果個又係<br />\n去到大英博物館個個剩係識打卡，冇幾多個香港人會靜心了解下文物背後既歷史同盛載住既文化<br />\n一係就影影影，要相既自己google啦，出自你親手影就係masterpiece好有紀念價值咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲衰過張張自拍，雖然都係戇鳩，自拍起碼有小小取代唔到既價值"},{"pid":"522d8a0c09446ebc1f8b1cba1793503fe6cbe6a3","tid":309591,"uid":84298,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"渣手機個d影，我都可以理解做share下fd睇下d展品有幾靚啊<br />\n<br />\n連渣單反大機個d都影一餐，真心睇唔透。拎黎聞?"},{"pid":"e4f675b80c8b594c582f259d676579f1d980e664","tid":309591,"uid":8274,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>博物館唔係所有嘢都可以影</blockquote><br />\n有得影實影<br />\n唔准影都硬係要偷雞影<br />\n到俾工作人員阻止就流露出一個'相已影'既勝利樣出嚟，唔好意思都冇句就走"},{"pid":"1641367c728a66445d52120716ecb8be8ec112d5","tid":309591,"uid":35780,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"最正係忽然變晒古董監賞家，件件都要評下真假<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，對佢地黎講，件貨越貴就越代表係藝術品"},{"pid":"223ab6c22431fad72feff62e03c5a9ff3cd9b093","tid":309591,"uid":16676,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"真心影黎都唔知做乜<br />\n木乃伊... 影人副倌返去J 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca6e63cb2eb6fcdf4d8971d6f8924b914adc69c","tid":309591,"uid":8274,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最正係忽然變晒古董監賞家，件件都要評下真假<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，對佢地黎講，件貨越貴就越代表係藝術品</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n然後又要指點江山咁發表佢啲濕鳩世界觀，慘在問呢班廢老四大文明係乜都未必數得出"},{"pid":